{"tid":1449310,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你班香港人抵撚死 場活動輸咪撚怪人","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:52:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:29:33.000Z","uid":156632,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"acaaf650f1b556946d953ab533178eba31f817f8","tid":1449310,"uid":156632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:52:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我對示威者真係好撚失望 特別係非前線<br />\n唔係因為你唔勇武 <br />\n而係因為屌你老母閪tst<span style=\"color: red;\">企得後一後但渣撚實枝水唔肯讓 </span><br />\n仲好撚嬌嗲扭計咁叫我去廁所裝水<br />\n我屌你個肥閪八婆你企咁撚後tg射唔撚到黎架 <br />\n驚就咪撚扮英勇<br />\n滅tg唔撚係遊戲比你貪得意搶分架仆街 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔敢做就留返比敢嘅人 總之咪撚罷佔資源</span></span><br />\n<br />\n仲有 原來速龍衝之前大半個鐘已經好多狗黎左 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">後面成班得閒mon po唔撚同前線講不特只 <br />\n叫撚哂你班撚樣企鬆啲比前線跑 <br />\n你地唔撚聽</span></strong></span><br />\n手足咪比人捉撚哂囉屌你地老母臭閪 <br />\n落樓梯時仲差啲人踩人呀<br />\n<br />\n仲有轉場嗰陣響地鐵度屌黎屌去 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">屌你唔撚認同咪各做各囉</span><br />\n做咩咁撚柒響咁多cam之下互屌 </span></span><br />\n又矮又大聲嗰個講緊你呀 <br />\nEQ唔好咁撚低啦好撚丟架呀<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">如果呢場活動輸 你地呢啲懶懶閒冇貢獻 連傳遞訊息 遞水都唔做嘅通通有份造成</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n[red]我係好撚嬲 香港好多人都唔撚抵幫 </span>好多人都寧願焦土 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但我屌完就不計前嫌 唔會割蓆 <br />\n對唔住我語氣重但請大家<strong>將整體利益放最前</strong><br />\n<strong>唔好比人屌你提你而起扛</strong><br />\n<strong>因為我地得返大家咋 </strong><br />\n<strong>敵人係政權呀 忍都好捱都好 <br />\n屌落去呀求下你地</strong>[/green]</span></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有兩點tips比大家：<br />\n1）觀察到一啲企前線(因為要捉勇武)但唔幫手任何嘢嘅人相當可疑，大家請長期alert望左右有冇人可疑<br />\n2）將身分證同錢所有重要物品袋響身，就算比狗抆住背囊都可以除低背囊跑走(入面唔好放任何透露你身分嘅嘢)"},{"pid":"cd03846dd6c566214fcc7d15f450fcbf6a3fdaaf","tid":1449310,"uid":156632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:55:00.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"9537f0467160dc5104e52fc2665fb31e67146863","tid":1449310,"uid":156632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:56:04.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"059e23d0dc11a7106ba8c248f22c668ec12181c1","tid":1449310,"uid":156632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:56:19.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"c6ad40b152e7763ec4372ca62586d70867c62bd1","tid":1449310,"uid":156632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:58:35.000Z","msg":"721 <br />\n811"},{"pid":"4f511fbd8df0348c6f2adfc3bffb9ca96fcd1fa7","tid":1449310,"uid":156632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:58:47.000Z","msg":"721 <br />\n811"},{"pid":"a578ad4f65ca42ab0d097021526660aef6d5206c","tid":1449310,"uid":156632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:59:17.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"ecacfd7a04a76074cb95143b3982c37ebc4e30cc","tid":1449310,"uid":156632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:59:27.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"6bb41ac535abab23974d90912f61e9dc2fd099a8","tid":1449310,"uid":156632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:08:30.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"f29ea5afea7437231051a2c17a6611bc187580c1","tid":1449310,"uid":156632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:08:42.000Z","msg":"721 <br />\n811"},{"pid":"6d8c9a367a9d6e4ed5aa69286ecf9ac0916f1551","tid":1449310,"uid":156632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:08:52.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"458966aa7428f29aac980322f11860593b03d7b5","tid":1449310,"uid":156632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:09:04.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811"},{"pid":"17931713798c42c340315739d7919c85d0e401d6","tid":1449310,"uid":156632,"like":0,"d